title: DJ Shadow - Nobody Speak feat. Run The Jewels
song: Nobody Speak feat. Run The Jewels

facts.text: DJ Shadow = Josh Davis, sampling genius behind 1996's 100% sample-based Endtroducing!!
Run The Jewels: Killer Mike + El-P met voicing villains on Adult Swim's Frisky Dingo!
Killer Mike ran for Atlanta city council & endorsed Bernie Sanders in 2016 primaries!
Song dropped Oct 31, 2016 - just weeks after Trump's election shocker!
Standalone single NOT on DJ Shadow's album The Mountain Will Fall (also 2016)!
Video parodies US political debates devolving into TOTAL brawl chaos!
Noel Fielding of Mighty Boosh fame moderates the madness!
Brett Gelman (Fleabag, Portlandia) plays a shady candidate!
Baron Vaughn from Daily Show Nightly Show joins the political punch-up!
Directed by Sam Pilling, who helmed Beck's trippy 'Wow' video!
Premiered on Adult Swim - RTJ's cartoon network home turf!
#3 on Australia's Triple J Hottest 100 of 2016 - massive Down Under!
Peaked #13 on Billboard Alternative Airplay in 2017!
Lyrics blast pols: 'Nobody speak, nobody speak, nobody...' pure diss track!
El-P produced RTJ3, dropped free same month for Black Friday!
DJ Shadow's crate-digging unearthed a killer obscure funk loop!
Video shot in UK but roasts American election fever perfectly!
150+ million YouTube views - pop-up politics gone viral!
2016 era: Politics + hip-hop = ultimate rage-against-the-machine vibes!
